,"msg":"不過 又可以點樣解釋 個腦只係想用某隻手㩒而唔係用另一隻手㩒？呢個位 會唔會已經需要訴諸自由意志？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 9up"},{"pid":"352cb4598f31e15843e1d756fb83bc9418fe1d87","tid":722302,"uid":82639,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T15:37:27.000Z","msg":"好睇你點睇自由意志係咩。<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得自由意志係現實世界配合。（明明你係窮撚，你想買私人飛機，買唔起，咁算唔算有自由意志？）<br />\n<br />\n再另一個level, 你係3D世界活，你對4D世界唔了解，根本無能力思考4D世界係點，咁又算唔算？<br />\n<br />\n同人猜包剪揼，任你想出咩就出咩（假設你有手，有physical 能力做到個動作） 咁又算唔算？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得如果同現實世界割裂，人係有自由意志。"},{"pid":"3d3d6db57a7676c027c15820a2ca59afe4b26848","tid":722302,"uid":169034,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:10:40.000Z","msg":"你不如問泥個世界係由0開始還是1開始"},{"pid":"6a946ff21c63297cf82115b6d68b495ed99a53f5","tid":722302,"uid":15935,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:12:53.000Z","msg":"做緊FN final paper?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定係暑sem已經完咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27331be6bf62ddb75a37706191a89886f1a7dd4d","tid":722302,"uid":31368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T18:14:34.000Z","msg":"如果個答案係無都幾絕望下"},{"pid":"d966341f72ec28c6db54485c5d1083a222498674","tid":722302,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:02:19.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n<br />\nMatrix Reload Quote<br />\nNeo: &hellip; You already know if I'm going to take it.<br />\nThe Oracle: Wouldn't be much of an oracle if I didn't.<br />\nNeo: But <span style=\"color: red;\">if you already know, how can I make a choice?</span><br />\nThe Oracle: <span style=\"color: red;\">Because you didn't come here to make the choice. You've already made it. You're here to try to understand why you made it. </span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iPsMm5mALNc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiPsMm5mALNc&d=VG8A9p9VJnYnEt6ENIbQG0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2a665b93\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iPsMm5mALNc</a>"},{"pid":"87bdbb9ef4de7a1e0bc3bda9a33553e83f45b145","tid":722302,"uid":128229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:30:03.000Z","msg":"無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野一早定左<br />\n只係你覺得自己會追尋到"},{"pid":"1ad33adf7ed96f0a1cfd56ac4d2cb42d4a013f4e","tid":722302,"uid":52472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:36:00.000Z","msg":"以社會學嘅角度黎講冇<br />\n人天生就係會模仿他人嘅行為<br />\n加上我地往往都被一啲規條或者法律規限左我地<br />\n再加上身邊嘅人事對我地嘅反應<br />\n其實會潛移默化影響到我地嘅思想同諗法<br />\n當然唔少得價值觀同道德<br />\n人生就係由人與人之間嘅交錯而組成同建立<br />\n<br />\n如果要有百份百來自自己嘅意志<br />\n我諗唯一方法係與世隔絕<br />\n<br />\n打個比喻<br />\n我地定義燈係燈<br />\n其實冇受過教育嘅人係唔會知燈係咩 燈有咩用 燈點著<br />\n呢啲都係通過學習同交流所得<br />\n再吸引轉化成我地嘅意義同思考一部份"},{"pid":"39a7cb04c8a77675a88fa866a61cbb9d2ef477d0","tid":722302,"uid":52472,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T19:37:49.000Z","msg":"我諗歸根究底樓主要諗返嘅野係<br />\n咩為之自由意志？<br />\n點樣證明自由意志嘅出現？<br />\n自由意志係點樣誕生？<br />\n喺我地落到定義之前<br />\n大家比嘅答案同睇法都好唔同"},{"pid":"70aa8bfb04cd66b21a42a91f7e1336fb3114ad58","tid":722302,"uid":185782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T20:12:36.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n人嘅思考模式，意志同性格都係基於佢本身嘅基因同生活經驗而形成<br />\n而人一生中所做嘅決定同埋一切嘅思維係嘅於基因同生活經驗<br />\n就好似電腦咁有點嘅input就有點嘅output除非個program本身有random variable <br />\n但我諗應該冇人會覺得random variable係自由意志"},{"pid":"90613a2afad6afe0970a2f4e54c5ce7560edaa98","tid":722302,"uid":185378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T20:22:32.000Z","msg":"FN：重點係人有free won't <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65509d3d377373a7a6fa4fadef7a76f00d90db5","tid":722302,"uid":23115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy